# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# NimbusCart — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# Server
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173

# Database — Supabase (preferred for testing/production)
# Get this from: Supabase Dashboard → Settings → Database → Connection string → URI
DATABASE_URL=

# Database — Local fallback (used when DATABASE_URL is empty)
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=nimbuscart
DB_USER=nimbuscart_user
DB_PASSWORD=changeme
DB_SSL=false
DB_POOL_MIN=2
DB_POOL_MAX=20

# Redis
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_PASSWORD=
REDIS_TLS=false

# JWT
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret-minimum-16-chars
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# UPI Payment (Native QR — no Razorpay)
UPI_MERCHANT_VPA=merchant@upi
UPI_MERCHANT_NAME=NimbusCart
PAYMENT_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=300

# Bank Webhook
BANK_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your-bank-webhook-hmac-secret
BANK_WEBHOOK_ALLOWED_IPS=

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=info
